Class AnwSimpleResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.integration.utils.SimpleResponse
      • com.sap.integration.anywhere.AnwSimpleResponse

  • public class AnwSimpleResponse
extends SimpleResponse
    Class, which represents response of SAP Anywhere HTTP calls. It contains information about error code, url, message or parsed id from HTTP POST request.
